---
import { ChevronRight } from "lucide-svelte";
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 bg-muted/50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">About IMPHNEN</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          IMPHNEN (Ingin Menjadi Programmer Handal, Namun Enggan Ngoding) is a
          community for programmers who want to be experts but are reluctant to
          code. We embrace the irony and create a space where developers can
          relax, share humor, and learn from each other.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Our community thrives on sharing memes, practical tips & tricks, and
          valuable knowledge from experienced senior engineers - all with a
          touch of humor and understanding that sometimes, we all want to be
          great without putting in the work.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-xs p-6"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What We Share</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ChevronRight
                class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"
              />
              <span>Programming memes that hit too close to home</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ChevronRight
                class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"
              />
              <span>Shortcuts and hacks to minimize coding effort</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ChevronRight
                class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"
              />
              <span>Knowledge from senior engineers who've been there</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <ChevronRight
                class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"
              />
              <span
                >Support for when Stack Overflow doesn't understand your
                question</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
